window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A single mother, afraid to take a chance on love...</b></p> <p><b>A fierce warrior, just learning how to feel...</b></p> <p><b>When fate throws them together in the most intimate way possible,</b></p> <p><b>Will Isobel run from the Beast...or Bond with him?</b></p> <p>Isobel Yates is a single mom with no time for romance, but the Goddess has other plans for her.</p> <p>Hail is a Dark Kindred. Since emotions are outlawed on his home world, he is learning to feel now that he lives on the Mother Ship. Strong emotions are bad news, though—they bring out the part of his DNA that is Bolaxian Beast, a race of beings known for their fierce breeding lust. </p> <p>Isobel is afraid to trust the huge Kindred warrior with her heart and the safety of her young son but when fate throws them together, she has no choice. When Hail's beast comes out, will Isobel run from him…or bond with him? </p> <p>You'll have to listen to Bonding with the Beast to find out…</p> <p>*Please note: There is a bit of rough sex in this book—well, what can you expect from a book called Bonding with the Beast, right? : ) Anyway, I wanted to warn anyone who is bothered by this sort of thing and assure you there is also tender lovemaking as well. Please listen responsibly!*</p>"; 
